review_text: i switched to this bank from the other local one i had previously been doing my banking at. i decided to switch as it was closer to my home big mistake!!!  after my phone experience with them not once ....twice....but after  the "third time"  i was totally disgusted with the way they have their customer phone system set up!! when you call it goes directly to the main office with "no option " to speak directly to a certain branch!! ( ridiculous!) the recording automatically puts you in a " so called "q" then proceeding to tell you what call you are & your wait time!!!  well .... the 1st time i was caller #2 w wait time of 8 minutes (again ridiculous) 2nd time i was caller #6 w wait time of 14 minutes... 3rd & last time i was caller # 9 w wait time of 25 minutes!!! i felt as though i was calling a radio station to win concert tickets ... but w this bank you dont win anything!!! it was urgent that i speak w an employee as my debit card was stolen & it was being used racking up astronomical chargers in the meantime!!! dime bank is the worst bank ive ever dealt with.....never again!! after all the problems i had entailed with this "unprofessional " business i was done with them!!! so unacceptable & very unprofessional!!!
this is my local bank. I go there because, everyone that works there is very friendly, and they have been extremely helpful correcting problems  I have had in past banking situations
